| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3393 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 83b37906-e0ff-5c73-84a2-044dcbf2c539"
